{"id":"summaries/2021-09-08-grip-the-juice-out-of-life","title":"Grip the juice out of life","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Title-only one-line aphorism from September 2021 by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a>: <em>\"Grip the juice out of life.\"</em> Sits in the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/voluntary-adversity\">voluntary adversity</a> / <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/fear-of-not-doing\">fear of not doing</a> cluster as the urgency-flavored sibling phrasing.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/voluntary-adversity\">voluntary adversity</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/fear-of-not-doing\">fear of not doing</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/fear-of-not-doing","label":"Fear of Not Doing"},{"id":"summaries/2021-10-26-manifest","label":"Manifest"},{"id":"concepts/voluntary-adversity","label":"Voluntary Adversity"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
